  <brief_title>Ghrelin - A Possible Opportunity to Improve Appetite</brief_title>
  <acronym>Phase 3</acronym>
  <official_title>Ghrelin - A Possible Opportunity to Improve Appetite, Nutritional State, Metabolic Integrity and Physical Functioning in Cancer Patients With Progressive Weight Loss</official_title>
