  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is designed to evaluate whether ghrelin treatment can improve appetite in weight
      losing cancer patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Randomized study with follow up evaluations each month until preterminal state. Cancer
      patients will be randomised to either high dose or low dose of active treatment given as
      daily injection.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
